lead_paragraph: American Gerina Piller continued her sizzling recent form with a ball-striking clinic, hitting every green in regulation on her way to the second-round clubhouse lead at the Texas Shootout in Irving on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Perfect Piller Piles on Birdies for Second-Round Texas Lead
